channel.title: Artem's RSPS History
channel.description:
[b]About myself:[/b] My name is Artem. I am a Russian. However I live in Canada. I am currently 16 years old.
[b]Quadro 7 - First server:[/b] It was funded in summer 2010. It was mainly hosted for fun. I didn't had any Java knowledge. My English grammar was also horrible that time. Here is a video: http://m.youtube.com/watch?feature=c4-feed-u&v=9vG-Mc7ZuyY
[b]RuneX-Gaming - Second server:[/b] It was funded in winter 2010-2011. It did went successful with 200 players. However I was kicked by my own co-owner from my own server. Here is a video http://m.youtube.com/watch?v=7TNs-vPqZxw&desktop_uri=%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D7TNs-vPqZxw
[b]Others:[/b] I always had this reputation of a person that created 273738374 servers. I actually did had more than 20 servers which all failed. This was more of an experience not only java-wise. I took my path to client development as I always loved to work on the graphical side. I just hate work on pathfinding, combat, skills & other server stuff. I partnered with different people:
[ul][li]arham4[/li] [li]uncalled[/li] [li]iz3 legend[/li] [li]holy grail[/li] [li]AtomicInt_ (90% of all my 3858726394 projects)[/li] [li]other people I can't remember of[/li][/ul]
Here is some media of my work:
[img]http://img221.imageshack.us/img221/4165/37861977.png[/img]
[img]http://img690.imageshack.us/img690/1504/45716984.png[/img]
[img]http://img689.imageshack.us/img689/825/npct.png[/img]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/zs1Xr.png[/img]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/eeFxd.png[/img]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/7ggtL.png[/img]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/P7FZS.png[/img]
[img]http://i.imgur.com/TA2bauR.png[/img]
I actually learned a lot. My Java knowledge and English grammar were fulfilled with newer knowledge. But still a lot to come.
Also, I forgot to mention. I've worked for SoulSplit in the past. I've been the pre-Galkon developer at SoulSplit Ltd.. I was programming with Galkon(Josh Lipson).
[hr]
Please feel free to post any comments. I just love talking on this forum.
